                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8365" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1286</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2336 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大手拉小手，国资科迪一起走——科迪乳业退市到重整之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Big hands holding small hands, state-owned enterprise Kodi walks together - Kodi Dairy&#39;s delisting to restructuring path</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王静，张子怡，严梦瑶，迟晓晨，史佳卉，蔡文宇，于华文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河南科迪乳业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务危机；退市；重整动因；重整效应；3C战略三角模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financial crisis; Delist; Motivation for restructuring; Reforming effect; 3C strategic triangle model</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河南科迪乳业股份有限公司（以下简称“科迪乳业”）曾是河南当地的龙头乳企，但其仅仅在上市7年后就退市不免让人唏嘘。从被ST到退市仅仅经历了两年，在享受了“小白奶”带来的短暂高光时刻以后，浮沫散尽。从2019年开始，科迪乳业陆续受到拖欠奶农奶款、大股东挪用资金、财务造假、资金链断裂等负面因素影响，引发一连串债务和经营危机，最终于2022年6月被深交所终止上市，随后被债权人申请破产重整，国资对其出手相助,并在2023年完成重整。本案例描述了科迪乳业退市到重整之路，重点梳理了国资参与科迪乳业重整的动因和破产重整的效应，并从财务危机、退市、破产重整流程几个方面进行阐述。本案例重在启发学生对财务风险进行衡量，多角度思考企业重整动因及破产重整的效应；同时对旨在用破产重整解决财务危机的企业提供一定的参考价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Henan Kedi Dairy Co., Ltd. was once a leading local dairy enterprise in Henan, but its delisting after only 7 years of listing is regrettable. After enjoying the brief highlight brought by &quot;little white milk&quot;, the foam dissipated. Starting from 2019, Kedi Dairy has been affected by negative factors such as delayed payments to dairy farmers, misappropriation of funds by major shareholders, financial fraud, and fund chain disruptions, leading to a crisis. In June 2022, it was delisted by the Shenzhen Stock Exchange and subsequently filed for bankruptcy reorganization by creditors. State owned assets assisted it and completed the reorganization in 2023. This case describes the path from the delisting to restructuring of Kodi Dairy, with a focus on sorting out the motives for state-owned assets participating in Kodi Dairy&#39;s restructuring and the effects of bankruptcy restructuring. It also elaborates on several aspects such as financial crisis, delisting, and bankruptcy restructuring processes. This case focuses on inspiring students to measure financial risks, and to think from multiple perspectives about the motives of corporate restructuring and the effects of bankruptcy restructuring; At the same time, it provides certain reference value for enterprises aimed at solving financial crises through bankruptcy reorganization.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》、《企业并购与重组》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务危机的界定与表征；重整动因；重整清偿方式；重整流程；企业重整效应；财务指标的分析等</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
